Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:09.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:12.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:16.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:24.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:34.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:41.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:48.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:56.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:59.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:03.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:07.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.43,0:01:10.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:14.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:18.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:21.26,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:25.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.66,0:01:29.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:32.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:35.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:41.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:49.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:02:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final round of the\NDavy Back Fight is underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The epic battle between the two captains...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has finally reached a climax!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't... let you have...\Na single member of my crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if it costs me my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:38.05,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Epic, Heated Combat!\NThe Fateful Final Conclusion"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With great drive, Straw Hat Luffy\Ngets back on his feet yet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Even after countless knockdowns...\N--Luffy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he just gets right back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's unsteady on his feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's out of breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he still stands tall with a glimmer in his eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.97,0:03:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All for his friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Now this is a Davy Back Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so teary-eyed I... I can't see straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm moved to tears!\N--Afro dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Luffy! Luffy!...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Luffy chant comes up from the crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has there ever been any other foe\Nwho's given our boss so much trouble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you idiots think you're doing,\Ncheering the enemy on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Boss...!\N--Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.06,0:04:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Boss! Boss! Boss!...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch. I'll end this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow-Slow Beam Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to do better than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! He hasn't got\Nenough strength left to run?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand to watch Luffy like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! It's time to finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow-Slow Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our boss makes the first move!\NHe starts by slowing down a cannonball!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foxy Fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Megaton Punch with\Nthe speed of a cannonball!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll knock you out for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! Our boss's cannonball stunt flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going for the finishing blow\Naboard the Foxy Fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! He used a beam\Non you just before the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dodge as soon as you can move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I can move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beam wears off on Straw Hat\Njust a moment sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a present for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got him! All of his attacks nail Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Boss! Boss!...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?!\NHe didn't have to go that far!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're barely\Neven able to stand upright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's how you want it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll pound you until you stay down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megaton Nine-Tails...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such intensity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The combatants now exchange an\Neven more ferocious flurry of punches!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slaughter 'im, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their barrages don't stop!\NThey just keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow-Slow Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the...?\N--He stopped moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Straw Hat has been knocked down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Strike that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat is the one who's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what has transpired?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mirror! A mirror fragment\Nhas fallen from Straw Hat's hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was stuck... in my afro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from the mirror in your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Flail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eight seconds to go.\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be what I think it is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?!\NStart counting too! Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--Dunno! But it seems fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our boss is sent soaring!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray! Hurray! Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he lands...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...outside the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final combat round of the Davy Back Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has ended after a heated, epic\Nbattle between the two captains!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our boss's legendary record of 920\Nwins and 0 losses has been snapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievably, victory goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't... let you have...\Na single member of my crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if it costs me my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our boss... lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foxy Pirates versus...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't just sit there!\NThe boss needs our help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm going! Move!\N--I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This orthodox-rules, three-coin game\NDavy Back Fight is now over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:12:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, could you have been any more reckless?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit poking him so much!\NHe's seriously hurt, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.47,0:12:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--And this!\N--Afro power, my butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had us worried the entire time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afros really are powerful, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! He's conscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The game! How'd the game end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I won... Was it just a dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. You won.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was never worried in the least!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, I got no reason\Nto be a pirate for any other ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Boss!\N--You should really stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you tarnish my\Nlegendary undefeated streak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put 'er there, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Boss!\N--Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiteful Shoulder Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten the rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choose your 500 people already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! The final exchange awaits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper and Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He starts off with two obvious choices!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now who'll be next?! Hurry and decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us your pirate flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious! You'd strip\Nus of our pride just like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your sail.\NYou need it to go places, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wow! He's so merciful!\N--But our symbol's on there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you expect us to use the sail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need your pity! Just take what's yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since your mark is all we need,\NI'll draw a new one over it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way you can keep your sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat... You're such a...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:36.93,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fox"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wow, they're really grateful!\N--No, we ain't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have 497 more people to pick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rules are rules! You have to\Nchoose 497 people, like it or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww. Do I have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you do, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! A captain's orders are absolute... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. In which case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Good thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll choose, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Me?\N--Yeah. Everyone from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--...to you.\N--Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many people is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we have 500 in our crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so excluding our boss, Hamburg-san,\Nand Porche-chan, that makes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, 497 exactly! It's 497 people...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Captain Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! It's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats are victorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.27,0:15:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This concludes the Davy Back Fights!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:16:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the birth of the New Straw Hat Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Merry can't hold this many people...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to follow along\Nin the Sexy Foxy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sexy Foxy is my ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to see the three of you run\Nthis huge ship all by yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never gonna happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then! Jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So long, Former Boss!\N--Don't catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Brush your teeth!\N--Take a bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they ever stop being comedians?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your first job as members\Nof the New Straw Hat Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:17:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You can count on us!\N--Rubber Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all off the crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're kicking us out?\N--Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A captain's orders are absolute, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go back to your old crews,\Nor even to Split-Head if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Former Boss! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We belong with the Foxy Pirates after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. They won.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there. I won't ride on stilts ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can follow the village together now,\Nhowever many years it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:18:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You folks...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went and kicked their butts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing new.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so that's why you accepted their challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like you wouldn't have otherwise, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The thing can talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a thing! I'm a mooole!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mooole"? Like a mole?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:19:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the champion! Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not another weirdo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Champion of what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the world champion of hole-digging!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm challenging my own record as we speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of challenge has you\Nwrecking the old stilts guy's house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Old stilts guy"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look. This is a "mooole."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Littonto. I'm about to go for\Nthe stilt-standing world record.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Competing with the world is a long, hard road.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be gone a few days. The mooole\Nwill keep you company, though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you manage while I'm gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. But make sure you\Ncome back as a champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:20:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be? Are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Grandpa!\N--Littonto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed you! I missed you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went and grew so much\Nsince I last saw you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for worrying you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's your grandson?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed my grandpa so much,\Nand that devotion led me to hole-digging!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And before I knew it, becoming\Nthe greatest digger in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had become my greatest goal in life...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you became the champion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! "Shoot for the other side of the world!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like that! You sound\Njust like the old stilts guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, you're too kind!\N--That's not praise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, couldn't you follow your\Nholes to reach your village?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this great, old guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:21:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I don't know how to begin thanking you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Miss! I achieved my true goal,\Nall thanks to your insight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget what you've done for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care on your way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too! I pray for your safe journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Time for us to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Is the Log ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! We're good to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.57,0:21:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get movin', then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and snag us a shipwright!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go find a shipwright!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:22:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.98,0:22:09.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:12.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:18.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:20.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:29.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:32.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:35.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.05,0:22:37.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:40.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:43.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:46.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:52.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:55.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.07,0:22:57.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:00.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:08.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.17,0:23:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Umm... What am I doing again?\N--Who are these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I with a bunch of pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who what where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.22,0:23:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't tell me all your memories are...!\N--Oh, my head! My head!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.51,0:23:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you okay, Long-nose?\N--Oh, it's so itchy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.89,0:23:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, all of ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Was It Lost? Stolen? Who Are You?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.98,0:23:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
